	<article id="post-808" class="post-808 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-lix tag-shell">
		<header class="entry-header">
									<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.geroro.com/archives/808" rel="bookmark">linux下的正则表达式</a></h1>
			
			<div class="entry-meta">
							</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
					<p style="margin: 0in; font-family: Consolas; font-size: 9pt;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$# 是传给脚本的参数个数</span></p>
<p style="margin:0in"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$0&nbsp;是脚本本身的名字</span></p>
<p style="margin:0in"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$1&nbsp;是传递给该shell脚本的第一个参数</span></p>
<p style="margin:0in"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$2&nbsp;是传递给该shell脚本的第二个参数</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; font-family: Consolas; font-size: 9pt;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$@<br />
是传给脚本的所有参数的列表</span></p>
<p style="margin:0in;font-family:Consolas;font-size:9.0pt"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$* 是以一个单字符串显示所有向脚本传递的参数，与位置变量不同，参数可超过<span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0);">9</span>个</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; font-family: Consolas; font-size: 9pt;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$$<br />
是脚本运行的当前进程ID号</span></p>
<p style="margin:0in;font-family:Consolas;font-size:9.0pt"><span style="font-size: 18px;">$? 是显示最后命令的退出状态，<span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0);">0</span>表示没有错误，其他表示有错误</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; font-family: Consolas; font-size: 9pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="background:white">区别：@*</span></p>
<ul style="margin-left:.375in;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;
 margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in" class=" list-paddingleft-2"></p>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">相同点：都是引用所有参数</span></p>
</li>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">不同点：只有在双引号中体现出来。假设在脚本运行时写了三个参数（分别存储在</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">1</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">12&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">3</span><span style="font-family:STIXGeneral;font-size:10.55pt;background:white">）则</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">&quot;</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">3</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">）则</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">&quot;*&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;
     background:white">等价于</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:
     10.5pt;background:white"> “</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;
     font-size:13.85pt;background:white">1</span><span style="font-family:verdana;
     font-size:10.5pt;background:white">12&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:
     MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">3&quot;</span><span style="font-family:STIXGeneral;font-size:10.55pt;background:white">（传递了一个参数）；而</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">“</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">3&quot;</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">（传递了一个参数）；而</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">“@&quot; </span><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">等价于</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white"> &quot;</span><span style="font-family:MathJax_Main;font-size:13.85pt;background:white">1&quot;&quot;</span><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:10.5pt;background:white">1&quot;&quot;2&quot;<br />
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;$3&quot;</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
     font-size:10.5pt;background:white">（传递了三个参数）</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="font-weight:bold;background:white">例子一</span></p>
<pre class="brush:bash;toolbar:false">##dels.sh
echo&nbsp;&quot;number:$#&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;scname:$0&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;first&nbsp;:$1&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;second:$2&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;argume:$@&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;show&nbsp;parm&nbsp;list:$*&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;show&nbsp;process&nbsp;id:$$&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;show&nbsp;precomm&nbsp;stat:&nbsp;$?&quot;</pre>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="background:white">执行结果</p>
<p></span></p>
<pre class="brush:bash;toolbar:false">[@jihite]$&nbsp;sh&nbsp;del.sh&nbsp;1&nbsp;2&nbsp;3
number:3
scname:del.sh
first:&nbsp;1
second:2
argume:1&nbsp;2&nbsp;3
show&nbsp;parm&nbsp;list:1&nbsp;2&nbsp;3
show&nbsp;process&nbsp;id:21057
show&nbsp;precomm&nbsp;stat:&nbsp;0</pre>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="background:white"></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="font-weight:bold;background:white">例子二</span></p>
<p><a  onclick='return showpotonohref();'  ><img  onclick="zoom(this,false);"   style="cursor:pointer;" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.geroro.com/wp-content/plugins/ueditor/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif?resize=25%2C25" alt="复制代码" data-recalc-dims="1"/></a></p>
<pre class="brush:bash;toolbar:false">#!/bin/sh
num=$#
name=$0
echo&nbsp;&quot;number:$num&quot;
echo&nbsp;&quot;scname:$name&quot;
echo&nbsp;$0
echo&nbsp;$1
echo&nbsp;$2
for&nbsp;((i=0;
i&lt;$num;&nbsp;i++))
do
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;$i&quot;
done
echo
&quot;argume:$@&quot;
for&nbsp;key&nbsp;in&nbsp;$@
do
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$key
done
echo&nbsp;&quot;-----------------&quot;
for&nbsp;key&nbsp;in&nbsp;&quot;$@&quot;
do
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$key
done
echo&nbsp;&quot;-----------------------------&quot;
for&nbsp;key2&nbsp;in&nbsp;$*
do&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$key2
done
echo&nbsp;&quot;-----------------&quot;
for&nbsp;key2&nbsp;in&nbsp;&quot;$*&quot;
do&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$key2
done
echo&nbsp;&quot;show
process&nbsp;id:$$&quot;
cho
echo&nbsp;&quot;show&nbsp;precomm&nbsp;stat:&nbsp;$?&quot;</pre>
<p style="margin-top:7pt;margin-bottom:7pt;line-height:18pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;
font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333"><span style="background:white">执行结果</span></p>
<pre class="brush:bash;toolbar:false">[@jihite]$
sh&nbsp;del.sh&nbsp;a
b&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
number:2
scname:del.sh
del.sh
a
b
0
1
argume:a
b
a
b
-----------------
a
b
-----------------------------
a
b
-----------------
a&nbsp;b
show&nbsp;process&nbsp;id:23582
del.sh:&nbsp;line&nbsp;37:&nbsp;cho:
command&nbsp;not&nbsp;found
show&nbsp;precomm&nbsp;stat:&nbsp;127</pre>
<p></p>
